  "2026-05-09T13:58:33.242Z",unknown,"Remediation workstreams 3-6 completed: unified semantic corpus generation through shared helpers with provider-aware limits (openai cap 8000, ollama cap 3200), implicit non-explicit hybrid timeout handling now degrades to keyword mode with fallback warning, Sentry scrub logic now recursively sanitizes nested payload/path-bearing frame fields, and security scan rules now fail absolute home-path plus user@private-host leakage. Focused verification passed via node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/embedding-batches.spec.ts tests/unit/reindex-command.spec.ts tests/unit/search-cache.spec.ts tests/unit/search-command.spec.ts tests/unit/sentry-helpers.spec.ts (83 tests). Live validation evidence: synthetic probe issue PM-CLI-B stored [scrubbed_path] in title/context/tags and was resolved after validation; unresolved PM-CLI-A and PM-CLI-9 remain historical timeout events. Remote telemetry validation: public healthz endpoint returned 200, queue depth was 0 with 1 consumer, telemetry_events last 24h=3080 (start=1505 finish=1472 error=103); legacy /api/health redirect target still returns 404 and remains follow-up."
  "2026-05-09T14:09:21.094Z",codex-agent,"Final verification gate passed after remediation updates: pnpm build && node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage && pnpm quality:static && node scripts/check-secrets.mjs. Results: 87 test files / 1228 tests passing, global coverage 100% statements/branches/functions/lines, static quality gate passed, and tracked secret/path scan passed."
